                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-698-18690712 t18690712-698-punishment-95"></join>Three Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Lord Chief Justice Bovill.</hi>
